#### 1st question:

legend controls series by series.name. So you can make a legend btn control multiple series via setting those series with the same name (`_h` in the example bellow).
```js
option = {
    legend: {
        ...,
        data: ['_h', '-m']
    },
    series: [{
        name: '_h',
        id: '16_h',
        data: [ ... ]
    }, {
        name: '_h',
        id: '20_h',
        data: [ ... ]
    }, {
        name: '_h',
        id: '30_h',
        data: [ ... ]
    }, {
        name: '_h',
        id: '40_h',
        data: [ ... ]
    }, ...
    ]
}
```


#### 2nd question:

I am afraid it can not be implemented directly, but you can try to use multiple axis to simulate multiple lane effect.

